Text:
Get cue files here & split yourself using medieval cue splitter.


http://cuenation(.)com/?page=cues&folder=clublife

http://www.medieval.it/
How to use:

1. Download files(mp3 + cue) using cuenation links.
2. Place them both in one folder.
3. open using med. cue splitter.

OR

Open .cue using foobar2000 to get the tracklist without splitting.

cheers
